short_description.value: A simple workplace management platform to effortlessly book desks and rooms, manage your hybrid workplace, and unlock key workplace insights

long_description.value: Freespace is an intelligent workplace management platform that helps organizations optimize their workplaces, improve employee experience, and unlock key workplace insights. The platform offers a range of features, including desk booking, room booking, hybrid space manager, workplace analytics, and workplace occupancy sensors. With Freespace, organizations can create a seamless and frictionless environment, enable hybrid working, and easily manage change in their space. The platform is scalable, flexible, and secure, with 24/7 support and proactive monitoring to maximize uptime and data integrity. Freespace has helped numerous organizations achieve significant savings and improvements in their workplaces, including a global insurance leading firm that saved $100m through data-led real estate optimization.
